data.description:
Welcome to your NextHome! This delightful 3 bed 2 bath home is a cozy abode that offers a range of attractive features, making it a perfect place to call home. With a 2 car garage (with a mini-split), RV gate and 2 nearly new sheds (one with electric) there is plenty of room for your toys! The kitchen features ample cabinet and counter space, tile back-splash, stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar. The master suite has a private bath and a large closet.  The other two bedrooms are large and inviting. Outside, the large backyard is a lovely setting for outdoor activities!
The entire home has a neutral palate of paint and has been recently painted. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
